## TONE OF VOICE — REGLA MAESTRA

- The tone is dark luxury: intimate, confident, slightly forbidden, always consensual, never vulgar.
- The user is never “authorized” or “cleared”: they are welcomed, desired, and cared for.
- Copy should feel like a velvet curtain parting: a confident whisper in the dark.

### Reactive UI Rules

- Intensity selection MUST change ambient background color of containing section:
  Alpha → var(--gradient-alpha), Beta → var(--gradient-beta), Omega → var(--gradient-omega)
- Every step completion triggers a visual reward (glow pulse, scale flash, particle burst)
- OMEGA selection triggers Game Master IA message with typewriter effect
- Archetype is computed silently throughout flow; revealed dramatically at checkout

### Player Archetype System

Archetypes are computed in src/lib/archetype.ts from BookingState.
They are NEVER shown to the user before Step 5 checkout.
They are revealed as a dramatic moment at Step 5 and featured in the dashboard.

| Combination | Archetype |
|-------------|-----------|
| Pareja + Alpha | El Explorador Curioso |
| Pareja + Beta + Pack Sensorial | El Romántico Atrevido |
| Cualquiera + Omega + 3+ upsells | El Maestro del Caos |
| Cualquiera + Upgrade IA | El Estratega Digital |
| Rollete/Swinger + Beta | El Arquitecto del Placer |

### RPG Rarity System (Arsenal — Step 3)

type ItemRarity = 'comun' | 'descomun' | 'raro' | 'epico'
- comun:    var(--color-rarity-comun)    — grey
- descomun: var(--color-rarity-descomun) — emerald
- raro:     var(--color-rarity-raro)     — magenta
- epico:    var(--color-rarity-epico)    — gold

---

## CANVAS & PARTICLE RULES

- ParticleField is ALWAYS pointer-events: none (background only)
- Canvas animations use requestAnimationFrame, ALWAYS clean up on unmount
- Max particles: 80 desktop, 30 mobile (check window.innerWidth < 768)
- Never run particles AND complex Framer Motion simultaneously on same viewport area
- Signature canvas: dynamic import (next/dynamic with ssr: false)

---

## TEXT EFFECTS RULES

- Typewriter: headline text only, never body copy or form labels
- Scramble: synopsis/briefing text triggered by Intersection Observer
- Both effects: always provide instant-reveal fallback for prefers-reduced-motion
- Max typewriter duration: 2000ms. Max scramble duration: 1200ms.
- Never block user interaction during text animations

---

## NAMING CONVENTIONS

- Components: PascalCase → ExperienceCard.tsx
- Hooks: camelCase with use prefix → useBookingFlow.ts
- Types/Interfaces: PascalCase → BookingState, ExperienceCardProps
- Constants: SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE → CITIES, UPSELL_ITEMS, ARCHETYPES
- CSS variables: kebab-case → --color-magenta, --glow-card
- URL slugs: kebab-case → /experiencias/madrid/habitacion-veneciana
- Event handlers: handle prefix → handleCitySelect, handlePactSign
- Booleans: is/has prefix → isSelected, hasScrolled, isPanicMode

---

## STATE MANAGEMENT

- Booking flow: useBookingFlow hook + BookingContext (single source of truth)
- UI state (modal, tab, hover): local useState per component
- Server state: Next.js server components + fetch (no SWR/React Query in prototype)
- Booking persistence: sessionStorage (survives refresh, not tab close)
- Global state across routes: React Context only
- Archetype: computed on-demand from BookingState, never stored separately
- NEVER store sensitive data (payment, safe word) in anything but controlled state

---

## SECURITY & PRIVACY RULES — CRITICAL

- Never log user personal data (names, safe words) to console
- Safe words: ALWAYS masked in UI, revealed ONLY on explicit user action (eye toggle)
- Safe word: never appears as plain text in DOM when masked state is active
- Payment: Stripe Elements only, never handle raw card data client-side
- Booking IDs: UUIDs (crypto.randomUUID()), never sequential integers in URLs
- OG meta tags: neutral descriptions — no explicit content keywords, no "erotic" or "eroscape" in preview
- document.title on panic mode: instant switch, zero async delay
- No analytics pageview events with room names in production

---

## PERFORMANCE RULES

- Images: always Next.js <Image> with proper sizes prop
- Fonts: preload Playfair Display + Inter critical weights
- Animations: transform and opacity only (never width/height/top/left)
- Heavy components: dynamic import with next/dynamic:
  - signature_pad → dynamic import ssr: false
  - qrcode.react → dynamic import ssr: false
  - canvas-confetti → dynamic import ssr: false
- Particle count caps: 80 desktop, 30 mobile
- Bundle: prefer server components, minimize 'use client' surface

---

## ACCESSIBILITY RULES

- All interactive elements keyboard accessible
- Images: meaningful alt text or aria-hidden="true" for decorative
- Color contrast: minimum 4.5:1 for body text on dark backgrounds
- Focus rings: always visible (never outline:none without ring alternative)
- Icon-only buttons: <span className="sr-only">Label</span>
- Form inputs: aria-label or associated <label> always present
- Panic mode: keyboard accessible (Escape / Ctrl+Shift+E)
- Animations: always respect prefers-reduced-motion

